{"title":"Attach printer","date":"2019-10-08T07:37:59.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 8, 2019","L":"10/08/2019","MM-DD":"10-08"},"link":"2019/10/08/Attach printer","tags":["tips"],"updated":"2019-10-08T07:37:59.000Z","content":"<ol>\n<li>\n<blockquote>\n<p>查共享打印机所连接电脑的ip地址 通过：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">ipconfig</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>可获得打印机的本地ip。</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>打开要安装打印机的电脑，打开 <em>运行</em> ，输入 步骤1 所获取到的 ip 地址。（以 192.168.0.19 为例）</p>\n<p>`\\\\192.168.0.19`</p>\n<p>输入后回车</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>输入后，系统自动检索该IP地址下已经安装且共享的打印机型号，进入 <em>网络</em> 中查看。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>双击要安装的打印机，会弹出 Windows<em>打印机安装</em>，正查找驱动程序。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>查找结束，弹出提示安装打印机驱动，点击 <em>安装驱动程序</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装完成后，系统会自动弹出一个打印机的窗口，安装完成。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>可 Ctrl+P 打印文档测试一下。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>ps: 若是未成功，可能是没有开启网络发现。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Ubuntu: command doesn't work","link":"2019/10/10/Unable to execute command under ubuntu"},"next":{"title":"GPU manual for the poor","link":"2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor"},"plink":"http://thswind.github.io/2019/10/08/Attach printer/","reading_time":"214 words in 1 min"}